Subject: [PATCH] feat: add Etrade CSV/Excel import functionality

- Added core/etrade_parser.py to parse Etrade 'By Status' Holdings reports (supports both CSV and XLSX)
- Integrated custom column mappings: 'Vest Date' -> 'Buy Date', 'Sellable Qty.' -> 'Quantity', 'Purchase Date FMV' -> 'Buy Price'
- Added /api/upload-etrade endpoint in app.py to handle file uploads
- Updated UI with an 'Upload Etrade' button in the header
- Updated README.md to document the feature and instructions for obtaining the file from Etrade
